 *    We require d(root_v) such that the path from root_v to root_u has parity 0 (since root_u is the new root).
 *    Path: root_v -> v --w--> u -> root_u.
 *    Parity(root_v -> root_u) = d(v) XOR w XOR d(u).
 *    So, we set d(root_v) = d(u) XOR w XOR d(v).
